  "instructions": [
    "Preheat your wood-fired oven to 400°F (200°C).",
    "Mix egg yolks and flour in a bowl until well combined.",
    "Add softened butter to the bowl and mix until smooth.",
    "Add piccalilli and mix until smooth.",
    "Add olive oil, ginger, garlic, salt, and cayenne pepper to the bowl and mix until well combined.",
    "Spoon the mixture into individual mini cocotte vessels.",
    "Place the vessels in the preheated oven and bake for 12 minutes.",
    "Remove the vessels from the oven and garnish with chopped parsley.",
    "Serve warm and enjoy!"
